# Project Scope

This subdirectory (`cursor/`) is the Cursor AI implementation of the Zodiac Calculator.

- Work only inside `cursor/`. Do not read or modify sibling tool directories.
- Follow `REQUIREMENTS.md` as the source of truth for behavior and layout.

## Done means

- Requirements in `REQUIREMENTS.md` are met
- `pytest` passes with full coverage on public behavior
- No secrets or committed virtualenv artifacts
